# Note 1 Add Keplr Wallet Chrome Extension
#### [Made by Bill Norton with Scribe](https://scribehow.com/shared/Note_1_Add_Keplr_Wallet_Chrome_Extension__OcrBi4VJS3WyAqR2ErJyog)
This guide shows how to connect a Keplr digital wallet to the Synternet Blockchain Test Net. By following the detailed steps, users will have an active digital wallet ready to connect to the Synternet Test Net blockchain, obtain some free tokens and apply them to subscribe to and stream various blockchain (Ethereum, Bitcoin, etc.) events to your desktop.

1\. Activate "Chrome"

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/480d0537-8254-446b-a4d4-f27b998cada3/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=0,0&br_px=859,480&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=53,-21)


2\. Click "Settingsâ€¦"

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/f922d556-7adb-4c7c-8526-0d197b8e9cdf/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=0,0&br_px=859,480&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=108,46)


3\. Click on Extensions

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/3f5ecf18-7d96-49d6-bb6c-7ed6e8c54864/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=0,1068&br_px=859,1549&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=222,212)


4\. We will fetch our Keplr wallet extension from the Chrome Store

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/4602f56d-e537-4045-aa10-a449503e12fa/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=0,230&br_px=859,711&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=340,212)


5\. Click in the search bar

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/f7201641-0916-4385-8848-b863367c9cd5/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=495,0&br_px=1355,480&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,122)


6\. Type "Keplr"


7\. Click here

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/e7bf51d4-1f07-40fc-b89c-cbb03f9957f3/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=491,0&br_px=1351,480&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,196)


8\. select the keplr wallet extension

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/5fa2c48a-84a1-41d0-b5b0-8246490e9628/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=620,127&br_px=1480,608&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,212)


9\. and add it to chrome

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/6fd58c18-0690-4594-9bf1-f03befe41469/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=1162,67&br_px=2022,548&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,212)


10\. Click the Add extension button

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/2b1f97d6-713c-4b6f-8690-e9b677d24b2e/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=717,764&br_px=1577,1245&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,212)


11\. We now create a new wallet to connect to the Synternet blockchain

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/01a38e23-5d9d-4dc2-8a7f-8b50cbac3f72/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=663,886&br_px=1523,1367&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,212)


12\. The recovery phrase is in case you forget your password and need to recrete your wallet or simply move or copy it to other devices.

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/85cc44e9-d06f-4d96-87de-5a7e347be849/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=455,797&br_px=1315,1278&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,212)


13\. Copy the recovery phrase words

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/d1b88803-e08e-40e1-abe2-93777d75b425/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=714,1134&br_px=1574,1615&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,212)


14\. After jotting down the words

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/b48f4b89-d8f6-4bb5-939a-a90d46811cff/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=714,1134&br_px=1574,1615&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,212)


15\. givethe wallet a name - I'll call this one disposable wallet as it will only work for this demo

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/1319f6e9-8d17-4dda-87e8-3bdd73f51848/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=668,1047&br_px=1528,1528&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,212)


16\. save the wallet

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/1bdfab26-dd18-4526-affb-bef84ea49d85/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=663,1124&br_px=1523,1605&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,212)


17\. And we are done

![](https://ajeuwbhvhr.cloudimg.io/colony-recorder.s3.amazonaws.com/files/2024-11-06/aab079c6-098c-40b7-96de-03509f601d0f/ascreenshot.jpeg?tl_px=114,1015&br_px=973,1496&force_format=jpeg&q=100&width=860&wat_scale=76&wat=1&wat_opacity=0.7&wat_gravity=northwest&wat_url=https://colony-recorder.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/watermarks/FB923C_standard.png&wat_pad=402,212)
